org.apache.iotdb.tsfile.encoding.decoder

Class RegularDataDecoder

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.iotdb.tsfile.encoding.decoder.Decoder
      • org.apache.iotdb.tsfile.encoding.decoder.RegularDataDecoder
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    RegularDataDecoder.IntRegularDecoder, RegularDataDecoder.LongRegularDecoder

    public abstract class RegularDataDecoder
extends Decoder
    This class is a decoder for decoding the byte array that encoded by RegularDataEncoder. RegularDataDecoder only supports integer and long values.
    .
